graph TD
    User([User]) -->|Inputs Natural Plan| UI[Streamlit UI / ADK Playground]
    
    UI -->|Forwards Plan| SPA[Safety Policy Agent]
    
    subgraph Security Checkpoint Node
        SPA -->|1. PII Scrubbing| PII[Email/Phone/SSN Redactor]
        PII -->|2. Prompt Injection Check| INJ[Keyword & Command Scanner]
        INJ -->|3. Unsafe Road Guidance Check| SAF[Flooding/Barricade Rules Check]
        SAF -->|4. Audit Log Generation| AUD[JSON Audit Trail to Stdout]
    end
    
    AUD -->|If Violations Blocked| FF[Final Output Formatter]
    AUD -->|If Clean| CMD[Commander Agent]
    
    subgraph Multi-Agent Delegation
        CMD -->|Delegates Destination Plan| DRA[Destination Readiness Agent]
        CMD -->|Delegates Dining Plan| FPA[Food & Place Agent]
    end
    
    subgraph MCP Server Stdio Tools
        DRA -->|Queries Context| MCP[ATLAS MCP Server]
        FPA -->|Queries Context| MCP
        
        MCP -->|Tool| T1[atlas_weather_context]
        MCP -->|Tool| T2[atlas_aqi_context]
        MCP -->|Tool| T3[atlas_civic_signal]
        MCP -->|Tool| T4[atlas_places_search]
        MCP -->|Tool| T5[atlas_safety_rules]
    end
    
    T1 -.->|Telemetry| CMD
    T2 -.->|Telemetry| CMD
    T3 -.->|Telemetry| CMD
    T4 -.->|Telemetry| CMD
    T5 -.->|Telemetry| CMD
    
    CMD -->|Assembles Report| DSA[Decision Scoring Agent]
    DSA -->|Calculates Weighted Score & Reason| FF
    
    FF -->|Outputs JSON| Out[ATLAS Decision Score & Trace]
